  <!-- Section: Application Process -->
  <section id="application" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Application Process</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The UAE Golden Visa process is remarkably fast compared to other investor visa programs—typically 2-4 weeks from investment completion to visa stamp. The process is increasingly digitized, though some steps require in-person attendance.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={timelineColumns} rows={timelineRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Step-by-Step Guide</h3>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Complete Your Investment</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Purchase property worth AED 2M+, establish your business, or make qualifying investment. For real estate, complete the transaction and register with Dubai Land Department. Obtain title deed or business license as proof of investment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Obtain Health Insurance</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Arrange DHA/DOH-compliant health insurance before applying. Get the policy certificate showing coverage details. This is a mandatory requirement—your application will not proceed without it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Gather Required Documents</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Prepare: valid passport (6+ months validity), passport photos, proof of investment (title deed/license), health insurance certificate, and bank statement showing source of funds. Some documents may need attestation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Submit Golden Visa Application</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Apply through the ICP (Federal Authority for Identity and Citizenship) smart services portal or GDRFA (General Directorate of Residency and Foreigners Affairs). Pay the AED 1,150 visa fee. Many investors use PRO services to handle the application.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Application Processing</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Processing typically takes 2-4 weeks. The UAE government reviews your investment documentation, background, and eligibility. You may be contacted for additional documents. Approval is generally straightforward for legitimate investors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Complete Medical Fitness Test</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">After initial approval, complete the medical fitness test at an approved center. This includes blood tests and chest X-ray (standard for all UAE residents). Results typically same-day. Certain medical conditions may require additional review.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">7</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Apply for Emirates ID</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Visit a typing center or apply online for your Emirates ID. Provide biometrics (fingerprints, photo). Pay AED 1,000 for the 10-year ID card. The Emirates ID is essential for daily life—banking, phone contracts, hotel check-ins.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">8</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Receive Visa Stamp and Emirates ID</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Your residence visa is stamped in your passport at GDRFA. Emirates ID card is delivered or available for pickup within 1-2 weeks. Congratulations—you're now a UAE Golden Visa holder with 10-year residence rights.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
      <p class="text-blue-800">
        <strong>Family applications:</strong> Your spouse, children, and domestic staff can apply for dependent visas once your Golden Visa is active. Each family member needs their own health insurance policy. Dependent visas are typically processed within 1-2 weeks after your visa is approved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

